            <h2 class="title animation" data-animation="fadeInUp" data-animation-delay="0.2">A huge thank you to all of our Sponsors</h2>
            <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfJbeS9i50qzS13POPa12So_uu1ATSt8WGuJEr4Po1nHUPhJA/viewform" class="btn btn-warning animation" data-animation="fadeInUp" data-animation-delay="0.3" target="_blank">BECOME A SPONSOR</a>
